problem:
I uploaded 4 frames from a vehicle dash cam video. 
Determine the vehicle's change in heading direction between each frame and its previous frame.
Give your answer in degree values ranging between -180 and 180 degrees, with veer to the right being positive degrees and to the left being negative degrees.
Keep all degree values in one list. You should have 3 values in the list.

I uploaded 4 frames from a vehicle dash cam video. 
Determine the vehicle's displacement between each frame and its previous frame.
Give your answer in numerical values in meter unit.
Keep all displacement values in one list. You should have 3 values in the list.
